COMMAND LINE OPTIONS

-0 use 0-360 degree longitude range
-b list of bands
-B page size for velocity data in bytes
-d max time separation
-D use default spectrum
-f ASCII file listing global bins
-h time-step
-n number of data files to keep in RAM
-N N-hemisphere velocity field
-p base-path
-P use/retrieve PMD data
-r critical/max distance
-R "rawread"
-s byte-swap file
-S S-hemisphere velocity field
-t number of time-steps
-v verbose mode

